data.description: Rare find with NO HOA! Room for RV/Boat parking plus 2 car carport. Located minutes from Lake Lowell, Red Hawk golf course, shopping, parks, walking paths, and schools. Updated beautiful 4 bed, 3 bath 2190 sqft plus a family room and rec. room. Newly renovated open concept with vaulted ceilings and new LVP flooring. The kitchen has beautiful granite countertops with decorative tile backsplash, a breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances with double ovens. Dining area has large bay windows. Lots of storage throughout plus an added laundry area and utility room. Recently upgraded HVAC to commercial grade with a new thermostat. Upgraded the well pump to a 3/4 hp pump. Located on almost 1/2 acre with mature landscaping. Sprinklers have an auto drip system for trees. Large covered deck with hot tub connection, 2 sheds, playset with turf, sandbox, raised garden beds, chicken coop, and lighted basketball court. This private backyard is perfect for family time and entertaining. Too many features to list!
